data.title: Wii #0589 - The Dog Island (Europe)
data.meta_description: Wouldn't an island of dogs just have dog crap absolutely everywhere? Who is there to clear it up?
data.meta_site_name: GBAtemp.net - The Independent Video Game Community
data.text:
These dogs have unnatural big heads, and nintendogs proportions are realistic = this game suck and is for children and girls. If I've had a wii I would never try a game with dogs with heads so much pumped up.
